disturb
a
second
time
the
hush
of
the
sickroom.
A
sickroom,
indeed,
it
soon
ceased
to
be;
Mr.
Moore's
good
constitution
quickly
triumphed
over
his
indisposition.
In
a
few
days
he
shook
it
off,
and
resumed
his
duties
as
